  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_3' aria-label=\" Thammaraya and Another versus The State of Karnataka pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('3','2025','2025_1_948_960','2025INSC108'); ><font size='4'> <strong>THAMMARAYA AND ANOTHER<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>THE STATE OF KARNATAKA </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 1 S.C.R. 948</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 108</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010002472025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : VIKRAM NATH<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, SANJAY KAROL, SANDEEP MEHTA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether the conviction of the appellants-accused under Sections 201 and 302 read with Section 34, Penal Code, 1860 is sustainable. Headnotes&dagger; Evidence &ndash; Case based on circumstantial evidence &ndash; Prosecution relied solely on recoveries of articles allegedly &ndash; Conviction u/s.201, s.302 r/w s.34, IPC &ndash; Sustainability: Held: Unsustainable &ndash; Impugned judgments quashed, set aside &ndash; Neither the disclosure statements of the accused persons were proved as per law nor the prosecution was able to establish the factum of recoveries of<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 22-01-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CRIMINAL APPEAL No. 649/2013</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 3 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('3','2025','2025_1_948_960','2025INSC108','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('3','2025','2025_1_948_960','2025INSC108','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('3','2025','2025_1_948_960','2025INSC108');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('3','2025','2025_1_948_960','2025INSC108','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
